Another very important thing is both plates are connected by the band, you NEVER lose one of the plates! And finally, my wallets are finished with natural beeswax!
All these things guarantee that you can have very luxurious, strong and reliable wooden wallet!
So please when you choosing your wallet, pay attention to my listed points and choose the best wallet!

If you decided to choose this wallet you can ask to personalize it! (but please write me about it before you purchase it)

Traditionally eaten widely by Native Americans to promote excellent connective tissue health. This root has an affinity for injuries surrounding joints or spine. Assists one in feeling "juicier" and less "dried out".
Traditionally used for the emotional body when fluids so depleted that tears can't come and the emotion gets stuck. Moistens airways in respiratory infections. Lubricates your being at all levels.

Gathered in the wild of the Westen North Carolina where the Smoky Mountains meet the Blue Ridge Mountains. *Only the middle section of these roots were taken for use. I always replant the two end pieces of Solomon's Seal roots so that the plant may continue to live.*
(Fall 2017 Harvest)
Harvested 1/2 mile from the nearest road, which means the area was completely undisturbed and free of chemicals.
Tinctured in 80 proof alcohol within 3 hours of harvest, which means this is a FRESH plant tincture.
*FRESH PLANT TINCTURE is far preferable in herbal action on the body vs DRIED plant tincture. 80 proof vodka is also much softer on the body than higher alcohol content tinctures.

All of my tinctures are kept in a very large medicine cabinet and are always kept away from light and electromagnetic frequencies.
The image of the jar is the actual amount of Solomon's Seal Root tincture available. I never over-harvest an area and all of the tinctures are made in extremely small batches.

Buy with confidence that every aspect of this tincture has been carefully planned, harvested, prepared and stored.

This glitter agate MacBook decal in blue, yellow, mint and gold is made of vinyl and is sure to add a whole new element of style to your laptop. Each marble decal is hand designed using spray paint and glitter and then photographed and printed on premium high-quality vinyl.

*Please read all the details before purchasing*

Each laptop skin is made to stick like glue and won’t leave any residue. It’s easy to put on and easy to take off. You could probably even use your laptop skin as a plate, but we really don’t recommend doing so as it will stain the beautiful colour of the skin.

This Rise and Shine MacBook decal is made of vinyl and is sure to add a whole new element of style to your laptop. Each black laptop sticker is hand designed which is then put on high-quality removable vinyl. These decals are perfect for your laptop, windows, water bottle, wall or any flat surface.

data.post_content:
The perfect gift for every Bearded guy. This is currently our most luxurious Kit; read on to find out why.

This entire kit is stored within a Leather Dopp Kit / Toiletry bag hand made from UK sourced leather. The leather is full grain and vegetable tanned which has a rugged look. It is extremely hard wearing and will stand the test of time. The seams have been double stitched and it comes with a handy carry strap at one end. The attention to detail is brilliant. The bag alone retails for $55

Included in the kit:
***
Large 50ml smashproof aluminium bottle of Premium organic Beard Oil available in a choice of 3 skin types - Dry, Normal, or Oily (if you are not sure of which skin type, then ask us or go for Normal skin) and with our trademark Bosque fragrance - we haven't met anyone yet that doesn't love the smell - seriously!
***
60g Tub of Barbesco Organic Beard Salve available in a choice of 3 skin types - Dry, Normal, or Oily (if you are not sure of which skin type, then ask us or go for Normal skin) and with our trademark Bosque fragrance
***
Medium hold Organic Mustache Wax that doubles as a hair tamer - helps to control rogue hairs.
***
Barbesco Green Sandalwood & Ox bone comb. Anti-static and natural in every way, this comb is perfect for de-tangling and distributing our oils and salve through your mane.
***
Barbers scissors; trim your mustache and stray hairs like a pro with these stainless barber shears.
***
All in a large handmade leather toiletry bag with plenty of room for the rest of your gear.

***Huge savings when you buy in this kit - all items available individually in our store***

For more details about each of the products, please take a look at the individual listings in our shop.
